{"tid":1506021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[風險分析] 機場可以「和你塞」，但唔建議行入去","createTime":"2019-08-25T16:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T23:53:15.000Z","uid":135274,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"635ecb7cdd42a08193258e1bb96b284ccc095145","tid":1506021,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:44:10.000Z","msg":"1.「和你塞」既原理係<strong>機場交通依賴青馬大橋及機場快線</strong>，容易崩潰；同樣道理，當機場發生衝突，<strong>手足都未必有足夠既交通網絡逃走</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n2. 813機場一役顯示，黑警可以唔完全清場，<strong>但仍然衝入黎作出拘捕</strong>；加上港共越黎越無恥，<strong>唔可以排除機場發生衝突，甚至「送頭」既可能性</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n3. 機場<strong>最嚴重</strong>情況既風險比街頭戰高。現時速龍小隊組成包括機場特警，但佢地主力快速拘捕，所以會比較輕裝（亦解釋咗點解速龍落單時會輸俾手足）；<strong>但佢地返機場嗰陣，係可以按照恐襲規格，光明正大開真槍</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n注意機場不合作運動既原理係<strong>影響香港經濟</strong>，而機場既風險比大家想像中高。所以，多人嗰陣可以搞「和你塞」，但唔建議行入去。"},{"pid":"f22b8b45d580e140f99ea2a9ed6ecc5c3e5f25cd","tid":1506021,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:45:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6107427113f5c358d98e4a446ad41690183aedb","tid":1506021,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:46:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd990d7458f84d0537b91638ffb02b89bc5d7abe","tid":1506021,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:47:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ee11da32c255a070010a0be04bffae7414df70d","tid":1506021,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:48:58.000Z","msg":"塞交通only"},{"pid":"414a1d65176370556f5f0256a9f14e116cb72676","tid":1506021,"uid":219564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:49:37.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"b6fbf5bfd0b78f47b0004b4a80c19d0b0efcee7d","tid":1506021,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69becf720fab489e11e78cfeb15775b1de722971","tid":1506021,"uid":50238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-2